quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  23,51,Oh nina zithunywa! dlanini ezintweni ezinhle futhi nenze okuhle okulungileyo ngempela mina ngiyisazi salokho enikwenzayo
  23,52,Futhi ngempela lesizwe senu yisizwe esisodwa futhi mina ngiyiNkosi yenu ngakho-ke ngesabeni
  23,53,"Kepha balehlukanisa udaba lwabo phakathi kwabo (kwaba noqhekeko) babangamaqembu, wonke amaqembu akuthokozela lokho ayekukona"
  23,54,Ngakho-ke bayeke besephutheni ekudukeni kuze kube yisikhathi (esinqunyiweyo)
  23,55,Ngakube bacabanga ukuthi sibandisela ingcebo nabantwana
  23,56,"Sibasheshisela ezintweni ezinhle?, kepha ababoni"
  23,57,Ngempela labo abahlala besovalweni ngenxa yokwesaba iNkosi yabo
  23,58,Kanye nalabo abakholelwa emavesini eNkosi yabo
  23,59,Kanye nalabo abangayenzeli iNkosi yabo abahlanganyeli ekuyikhonzeni
  23,60,Kanye nalabo abaphanayo ngalokho abaphana ngakho kulapho izinhliziyo zabo zigcwele ukwesaba ukuthi bona baqinisekile ukubuyela eNkosini yabo
  23,61,Bayilabo abaphuthuma emisebenzini emihle futhi bona bayancintisana ngayo
  23,62,Futhi umphefumulo asiwethwesi umthwalo ongaphezu kwamandla awo ngaphandle kokuwulingene futhi kuthina kunencwadi ekhuluma iqiniso futhi bona abenziwa okungenabulungiswa
  23,63,Kepha izinhliziyo zabo zimboziwe mayelana nalokhu futhi okwabo izenzo ezingale kwalokho bona abakwenzayo
  23,64,Kuze kube yilapho sibabamba ngesijeziso labo abaphila impilo entofontofo phakathi kwabo bheka! Bona bayazehlisa bayakhala bacela usizo
  23,65,Musani ukukhala namhlanje ngempela nina aninasizo oluvela kuthina
  23,66,Ngaphambilini nanifundelwa amavesi ami kepha nanijwayele ukuwafulathela ngezithende zenu
  23,67,Ngokuziqhenya nichitha ubusuku nikhuluma okubi ngawo
  23,68,Ngakube abadlinzi yini ngezwi na? Noma ngakube kwabafikela lokho okungazange kufike kobaba babo basendulo yini na
  23,69,Noma ngakube abazange basazi yini isithunywa sabo ukuthi bangaze basiphike na
  23,70,Noma bakhuluma ngaso bathi siyahlanya na? Kepha sabafikela neqiniso futhi iningi labo liyalizonda iqiniso
  23,71,"Futhi uma iqiniso (u-Allah) lingalandela izifiso zabo, amazulu nomhlaba kwakuzokonakala, nanoma ngabe ngubani okhona kuwona. Kepha sabanika isikhumbuzo sabo babe sebeyasifulathela isikhumbuzo sabo"
  23,72,Noma ngakube ubacela umvuzo yini na? Kepha umvuzo weNkosi yakho muhle ungcono futhi yona ingcono kakhulu kunabo bonke abondli
  23,73,Futhi ngempela wena ubamemela endleleni eqondile
  23,74,Futhi ngempela labo abangakholelwa empilweni ezayo ngempela basekuphambukeni endleleni
  23,75,Futhi noma ngabe sasibe nomusa kubona futhi sayisusa inhlupheko abanayo ngempela babezoqhubeka nokona bephuphutheka
  23,76,Futhi ngempela sababamba ngesijeziso kepha abazange bazehlise eNkosini yabo futhi abazange bazithobe
  23,77,Kwaze kwaba yilapho sesibavulela isango lesijeziso esinzima kulapho bona bephelelwe yithemba lapho